# textdomain: mcl_beds
Beds allow you to sleep at night and make the time pass faster.=I letti ti permettono di dormire di notte e velocizzano il passaggio del tempo.
To use a bed, stand close to it and right-click the bed to sleep in it. Sleeping only works when the sun sets, at night or during a thunderstorm. The bed must also be clear of any danger.=Per utilizzare un letto, stagli vicino e cliccaci col tasto destro per dormirci. Puoi dormire solo quando il sole cala, di notte o durante una tempesta. Occorre anche eliminare qualsiasi pericolo vicino al letto.
You have heard of other worlds in which a bed would set the start point for your next life. But this world is not one of them.=Sei venuto a conoscenza di altri mondi dove un letto definirebbe il punto di partenza per la tua prossima vita. Ma questo mondo non Ã¨ uno di quelli.
By using a bed, you set the starting point for your next life. If you die, you will start your next life at this bed, unless it is obstructed or destroyed.=
In this world, going to bed won't skip the night, but it will skip thunderstorms.=
Sleeping allows you to skip the night. The night is skipped when all players in this world went to sleep. The night is skipped after sleeping for a few seconds. Thunderstorms can be skipped in the same manner.=
